page.title: 12AT HOME
page.content: MY MUM WAKES ME UP AT 7.30 AND IGET DRESSED AND HAVE MY BREAKFAST.I LIKE TO EAT FROSTIES BEST.THEN IHAVE A WASH AND BRUSH MY HAIR AND CLEAN MY TEETH.THEN I GO TO SCHOOL AT 8.30.I COME HOME AT 3.30.SOMETIMES I GO TO MY FRIND'S HOUSE OR SOMETIMES THEY COME TO MY HOUSE.WE PLAY ALL SORTS OF GAMES WE PLAY WITH MY TEDDIES,OR WE PLAY DRESSING UP OR WEPLAY ON OUR BIKES.MY MUM COMES HOME FROM WORK AND WE HAVE TEA AT ABOUT 6 O'CLOCK.I LIKE TO WATCH TELEVISION,ESPECIALLY CARTOONS TILL MY DAD WATCHES THE NEWS.IN SCHOOL TIMES IHAVE TO GO TO BED AT 8O'CLOCK BUT I CAN READ MY BOOKS AND COMICS FOR A WHILE.
